UPDATE applicants SET gpa = 3.5, major = 'Finance Major, Economics Minor', expected_graduation = 'Class of 2028', linkedin_url = 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/nnadozie-okasi/', why_hillside = 'I find Hillside Ventures to be particularly intriguing as it offers a hands-on approach to venture capital investing that goes beyond the realm of conventional academic theory. Unlike most finance courses that offer students the opportunity to work in situations with actual responsibility in assessing early-stage companies, Hillside Ventures promises to provide such an opportunity. The prospect of working with driven entrepreneurs to assess the viability of their ideas as they develop into successful companies is particularly intriguing to me. The structured approach to the work environment, combined with the actual responsibility to perform at a high level, makes Hillside Ventures a unique opportunity for students to work in an environment where they are treated as professionals.

